    "en": {
      "title": "800 repaired Langama buses are running from August",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Transport Minister Dr. Bandula Gunawardena said that 800 additional buses from 105 depots of Lanka Transport Board (Langama) will be put into operation from August 1st.",
        "The Minister of Transport Bandula Gunawardena said that 800 buses which had been taken out of service due to the lack of tires and spare parts will be repaired and put back into service. ."
      ],
